c: 39
v: 6
t: "Niyo yabaremye mu mutima umwe, hanyuma igira mugenziwe kuba nkawe nukuba manurira ibikoko umunani harimwo impfizi n’inyana, rero ibarema munda z’abavyeyi banyu mufise iremwa ritandukanye n’irindi, riri mumyijima itatu, iyo rero niyo Mana ariyo Muremyi wanyu, ubwami bwose ni rwiwe kandi ntawundi asengwa bimwe vy’ukuri atariyo yonyene gusa, none mwebwe muhindukizwa hehe"